welcome_message_body: Welcome to Eden Prairie, where you'll find a perfect blend of natural beauty and modern amenities. Known for its picturesque lakes, vibrant parks, and friendly community, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our charming city has to offer.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal of Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal primarily used by budget airlines and for regional flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Flying Cloud Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Jet Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to private jet flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free wifi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Crystal Airport handles all commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Crystal Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing exclusive services and facilities for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport serves domestic flights for various airlines.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The international terminal at Downtown Airport serves international flights for select airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Anoka County–Blaine Airport handles all commercial flights and services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Anoka County–Blaine Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
